                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8586" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1326</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2585 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">借力展翅，拨云见日 ——俯瞰“猪王”正邦科技破产重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Harnessing Strength to Spread Its Wings, Clearing the Clouds to See the Sun — A Bird&#39;s-eye View of the Bankruptcy Reorganization Journey of &quot;Pig King&quot; Zhengbang Technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李银香，徐嘉怡，罗冰冰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西正邦科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">28 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整；正邦科技；重整投资人；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bankruptcy Reorganization、Zhengbang Technology、Reorganization Investor</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了江西曾经民营第一股——“江西猪王”正邦科技，经历迅猛发展与激进扩张后，举债经营，适逢行业周期下行遭遇连续巨亏，导致资不抵债步入破产重整。在此困境下，公司增发股份引入双胞胎信达联合体作为重整投资人注入现金43.4亿元，并且调整经营计划，进行全方位的资源赋能，最终借助重整投资人之力摆脱困境的经历。本案例引导学生深入系统探究破产重整的原因及法律要求，熟悉重整价值的判断方法，知悉破产重整的模式与具体措施，并进一步剖析企业陷于财务困境的原因和重整投资人的作用，评估破产重整对利益相关者的不同影响，深化学生全面理解破产重整对企业走出困境实现高质量发展的重要作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the experience of Zhengbang Technology, once the leading private company in Jiangxi known as the &quot;King of Pigs,&quot; which after rapid development and aggressive expansion, operated on debt. Consequently, amid a downturn in the industry cycle, it faced consecutive huge losses, leading to insolvency and entering bankruptcy reorganization. In this predicament, the company issued additional shares to introduce the Twins-Cinda Consortium as the restructuring investor, injecting 4.34 billion yuan in cash. Additionally, it adjusted its business plan and carried out comprehensive resource empowerment. Ultimately, with the help of the restructuring investor, it managed to overcome its difficulties. This case guides students to systematically explore the reasons for bankruptcy reorganization and legal requirements, familiarize themselves with the methods of determining reorganization value, understand the models and specific measures of bankruptcy reorganization, and further analyze the causes of corporate financial distress and the role of restructuring investors. It also assesses the different impacts of bankruptcy reorganization on stakeholders, deepening students&#39; comprehensive understanding of the important role of bankruptcy reorganization in helping enterprises overcome difficulties and achieve high-quality development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《并购与重组》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整；财务困境；营运价值理论；重整价值；重整投资人；资源依赖理论；破产重整模式；破产重整措施；利益相关者理论；重整效果</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
